@startuml SSD_UC3_LoginLogout
' System Sequence Diagram - UC3 Effettuare login e logout
title SSD - UC3 Effettuare login e logout

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam participant {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor white
}

actor "User" as U
participant "System\n:NerdVault" as S

U -> S : apriLogin()  <GET /auth/login>
activate S
S --> U : form di login
deactivate S

U -> S : login(email, password, csrfToken)  <POST /auth/login>
activate S
S --> U : sessione creata (ruolo, id, username) + redirect area utente/admin
deactivate S

U -> S : logout(csrfToken)  <POST /auth/logout>
activate S
S --> U : sessione distrutta + redirect home
deactivate S

note over U, S
  Alternative: credenziali non valide, account bannato,
  email non verificata, sessione scaduta per inattivita
  (> 30 min) -> redirect login con messaggio dedicato
end note
@enduml
